<div id="logo-guide" class="flexbox vertical center"> 
  <div class="page-header flexbox vertical center">
    <div class="inner flexbox vertical flex-1">
      <div class="flexbox horizontal center flex-1">
        <div class="title flexbox vertical start">
          <div class="line-a">
            Logo Guide
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="page-section flexbox vertical stretch flex-1">
    <div class="inner flexbox vertical stretch">
      <div class="headline">
        AnyKey assets and brand identity guide
      </div>
      <div class="flexbox horizontal center wrap justify-space-around">      
        <div class="intro-section">
          <p>Our name, a playful reference to the phrase “press any key to continue,” was chosen to convey the idea that anybody should be welcome in gaming.</p>
          <p>Our logo, a mechanical keycap with an equality sign, was designed to represent that elusive key.</p>
          <p>The AnyKey was created as a universal symbol of respect and inclusion. We ask anyone who uses it as a sign of welcome to follow a few simple guidelines.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="logo-schematic">
          <%= image_tag("/images/anykey-logo-schematic.png") %>
        </div>  
      </div>  
    </div>
  </div>
  
  
  <div class="page-section flexbox vertical stretch">
    <div class="inner flexbox vertical stretch">
      <div class="flexbox horizontal center wrap justify-space-around">

        <div class="flexbox vertical start">
          <div class="flexbox vertical center">
            <div class="downloadable-logo white-background">
              <%= image_tag("/images/anykey-logo-black.png") %>
            </div>
            <div class="logo-links">
              <%= link_to("EPS", image_path("/images/anykey-logo-black.eps"), target: "_blank", class: "inline") %> • <%= link_to("PNG", image_path("/images/anykey-logo-black.png"), class: "inline", target: "_blank") %>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flexbox vertical center">
            <div class="downloadable-logo black-background">
              <%= image_tag("/images/anykey-logo-white.png") %>
            </div>
            <div class="logo-links">
              <%= link_to("EPS", image_path("/images/anykey-logo-white.eps"), target: "_blank", class: "inline") %> • <%= link_to("PNG", image_path("/images/anykey-logo-white.png"), target: "_blank", class: "inline") %>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flexbox vertical center">
            <div class="downloadable-logo green-background">
              <%= image_tag("/images/anykey-logo-green.png") %>
            </div>
            <div class="logo-links">
              <%= link_to("EPS", image_path("/images/anykey-logo-green.eps"), target: "_blank", class: "inline") %> • <%= link_to("PNG", image_path("/images/anykey-logo-green.png"), target: "_blank", class: "inline") %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        
        <div class="usage-section flexbox vertical start">
          <div class="section-title">
            Using the AnyKey logo
          </div>
          <div>
            <p>Here goes text about how to use the assets.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
</div>